## CPU & Memory Basics

### CPU Architecture
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│           CPU (Multi-Core)          │
│                                     │
│  ┌─────────┐      ┌─────────┐      │
│  │ Core 1  │      │ Core 2  │      │
│  │ L1 Cache│      │ L1 Cache│      │
│  └─────────┘      └─────────┘      │
│       └──────┬────────┘            │
│           L2/L3 Cache              │
└──────────────┼──────────────────── ┘
               │
            RAM (Heap)
```

### Memory Access Flow
```
CPU → Cache (L1/L2/L3) → RAM (Heap)

CPU first checks Cache for data
If not found (cache miss) → fetches from RAM (slower)
Frequently accessed objects get cached automatically
```

